Description: Simulation, three-step estimation, diagnostic testing, detrending,
    and data preparation tools for noncausal autoregressive models driven by
    causal GARCH(1,1) volatility. The methods are associated with the CREST
    working paper "Noncausal AR processes driven by causal GARCH volatility"
    by Velasquez-Gaviria and Zakoïan (2026).
